AUTHORSHIP AND ATTRIBUTION
───────────────────────────

Application framework, story world, plot, narrative design, and the three story
scenarios (QLAB-7 / The Glass Archive / Sector Null) were created by Zhengming Yu
with AI-assisted development by Claude (Anthropic).

The quantum rules engine (quantum_rules.py) and the LLM prompt template
(prompt_template.txt — system prompt, Rules 1–8, Quantum Language Guide,
turn prompt structure, and generate_narrative() pattern) were authored by
Samhitha Kondeti and and 'prompt_template.txt' integrated by Hitha Magadi Vijayanand,'quantum_rules.py' integrated by Bari Vadaria for CSCE 656-600 Computer
New Media at Texas A&M University, with Flask route integration by Zhengming
Yu and Carrigan Royer. These components are not covered by this license for
redistribution — please obtain them through the original course materials. It defines the
game's core mechanical layer (intent parsing, action validation, quantum
effects, win/loss evaluation) and is not covered by this license for
redistribution — please obtain it through the original course materials.

